title: GoTo Jumps in Trading Debut After Indonesian Tech Giant’s IPO Raises $1.1 Billion - The Wall Street Journal
content: GoTo Jumps in Trading Debut After Indonesian Tech Giant’s IPO Raises $1.1 Billion  The Wall Street Journal
description: Shares of Indonesia’s ride-hailing, e-commerce and financial services company closed above their IPO price, catapulting the company into the ranks of the country’s most valuable stocks.
